      • main

        public static void main(String[] args)
                 throws Exception
        Serialize the profile to a file.
        Parameters:
        args - Expects two arguments args[0] is the name of a file, and args[1] is a RIOT name for a serialization format (an RDFFormat, e.g. TURTLE_PRETTY).
        Throws:
        Exception - if we can't write teh serialized profile to the file
